      • getLexicalEntries

        public List<LexicalEntry> getLexicalEntries(String word,
                                   EPartOfSpeech pos,
                                   Lexicon lexicon)
        Searches for lexical entries for given word. Optionally the words can be filtered by part-of-speech and lexicon
        Parameters:
        word - Word to search
        pos - If not null, filters lexical entries by part-of-speech given by the Enum element
        lexicon - If not null, filters lexical entries by lexicon. Note that the Lexicon object has to be obtained beforehand
        Returns:
        A list of LexicalEntry objects which mathc the criteria
